            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Error is Reported by Authors are Purely",
                "Statistical.The Systematic Errors in Polarization,",
                "Caused by the Calibration Procedure,Imply a Fractional",
                "Uncertainty of About 5%.The True Spectrometer 0 Degree",
                "Position is Uncertain to Within 0.1 Degree.Contribution",
                "From Adjacent Levels and General Background were not",
                "Subtracted.With the Aid of Measured Spectra these",
                "Contributions were Estimated to be Less Than 10% For",
                "All Angles Except For 11 Degree Where the Background",
                "Contributions to the 7.65 MeV Level were About 20%."
              ]
            }
